The Osun State Governorship Election Tribunal has declared the Ademola Adeleke of the Peoples Democratic Party as the duly-elected governor of Osun state. The tribunal sacked Isiaka Oyetola of the All Progressive Congress, APC. Osun guber poll: Tribunal voids cancellation of election in 7 polling units Osun Guber Poll: Tribunal upholds PDP's claims of alteration of results Tribunal reserves judgement in Osun governorship election petition